Dominic Chianese https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dominic_Chianese 0 Dominic Chianese (born February 24, 1931) is an American actor, singer, and musician. He is best known for his role as Corrado "Junior" Soprano on the HBO series The Sopranos, and Johnny Ola in The Godfather Part II.
